<blockquote><div><cite>hiplop wrote:</cite><div style="display:inline;font-style:italic">hiplop where'd your neuky town read come from?</div><br>
Neuky has seemed towny the entire time, hes the one im least confident in though, to be honest.</div></blockquote> - I don't understand this. Please clarify. my thoughts are how can I appear towny "the entire time", while I'm also the one you are least confident in.  Remember that Faraday declared me town, and waited to see if you sheeped his thoughts?  This is what I think you did here, but decided to qualify it at the end of your statement.

